Iron Will;;1994;;PG;;Adventure,Family;;6.6;;Charles Haid;;Mackenzie Astin,Kevin Spacey,David Ogden Stiers,August Schellenberg,Brian Cox,George Gerdes,John Terry,Penelope Windust,Jeffrey Alan Chandler,Michael Laskin,James Cada,Rex Linn,Allan R.J. Joseph,Alvin William 'Dutch' Lunak,Tony Griffin,Jeff Hochendoner,Rusty Hendrickson,Richard Riehle;;When Will Stoneman's father dies, he is left alone to take care of his mother and their land. Needing money to maintain it, he decides to join a cross country dogsled race. This race will require days of racing for long hours, through harsh weather and terrain. This young man will need a lot of courage and a strong will to complete this race.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0110157/